 Beweging.net brings together a large network of social organizations and thousands of volunteers.
Together, we seek equitable solutions to social challenges. We act, we set up projects and we try to change things so that everyone can live in a decent and agreeable way. We do this by paying particular attention to the most vulnerable. “”Beweging.net West Flanders” already has experience in setting up new projects such as the Fietsbieb (Leader project) or the cork project (with the support of the province of West Flanders).
